  "texts": [
    "Slight differences in the code labels between human codes and AI codes were observed.",
    "However, in the end, human codes were fewer because some of the codes were combined with similar codes referring to the same function or meaning. 5.",
    "Categorizing into bigger overarching themes.",
    "The coded categories of survey responses were further categorized into overarching themes in the final stage.",
    "The Discourse Analyzer AI toolkit was utilized to extract overarching themes from the dataset (see Tables 4 and 5 for the overarching themes extracted by AI)."
  ]
}